msgstr "File/Directory"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "作用"
msgstr "Role"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "是否生成 ``dict.txt``"
msgstr "Generates ``dict.txt``"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "主词典：包含所有已知词汇及其频率"
msgstr "Main dictionary: contains all known words and their frequencies"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "❌ 静态文件，人工维护 ``finalseg`` /"
msgstr "❌ Static file, manually maintained ``finalseg`` /"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "HMM"
msgstr "HMM"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "模型参数：用于未登录词识别"
msgstr "Model parameters: used for out-of-vocabulary word recognition"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "⚠️  ``.py``  从 ``.p`` 转换而来 ``posseg/``"
msgstr "⚠️ ``.py`` converted from ``.p`` ``posseg/``"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "词性标注模型参数"
msgstr "Part-of-speech tagging model parameters"

#: ../../rel_txt.csv:1
msgid "⚠️ ``.py`` 从 ``.p`` 转换而来"
msgstr "⚠️ ``.py`` converted from ``.p``"

#: ../../04-data.rst:36
msgid "工作流程："
msgstr "Workflow:"

#: ../../04-data.rst:53
msgid "加载过程："
msgstr "Loading Process:"

#: ../../04-data.rst:55
msgid "资源文件加载过程："
msgstr "Resource File Loading Process:"

#: ../../04-data.rst:57
msgid "首次运行时，从 ``dict.txt`` 读取所有词条"
msgstr "On the first run, read all entries from ``dict.txt``"

#: ../../04-data.rst:58
msgid "构建前缀树结构（包含所有词及其前缀）"
msgstr "Build a prefix tree structure (containing all words and their prefixes)"

#: ../../04-data.rst:59
msgid "缓存到 ``jieba.cache`` 文件（ ``marshal`` 格式），加速后续加载"
msgstr "Cache to the ``jieba.cache`` file (in ``marshal`` format) to speed up subsequent loads"

#: ../../04-data.rst:60
msgid "分词时使用前缀树快速匹配"
msgstr "Use the prefix tree for fast matching during segmentation"

#: ../../04-data.rst:64
msgid "总结"
msgstr "Summary"

#: ../../04-data.rst:66
msgid "``dict.txt`` 是核心词典，静态文件，非生成"
msgstr "``dict.txt`` is the core dictionary, a static file, not generated"

#: ../../04-data.rst:67
msgid "``finalseg``/ 和 ``posseg``/ 是统计模型参数，用于增强分词能力"
msgstr "``finalseg``/ and ``posseg``/ are statistical model parameters used to enhance segmentation capabilities"

#: ../../04-data.rst:68
msgid "三者配合工作：词典负责已知词，HMM 负责未知词，\\ ``posseg`` 负责词性标注"
msgstr "The three work together: the dictionary handles known words, HMM handles unknown words, and ``posseg`` handles part-of-speech tagging."

#: ../../04-data.rst:69
msgid "这种设计让 ``jieba`` 既能准确切分常见词，又能智能处理新词"
msgstr "This design allows ``jieba`` to both accurately segment common words and intelligently handle new words."
